[00:00.52]	[London. QUEEN KATHARINE's apartments.,]
[00:01.58]	[Enter QUEEN KATHARINE and her Women, as at work]
[00:02.64]QUEEN KATHARINE	Take thy lute, wench: my soul grows sad with troubles;
[00:07.76]	Sing, and disperse 'em, if thou canst: leave working.
[00:12.61]	[SONG]
