[00:52.90]	[Enter a Gentleman]
[00:53.96]QUEEN KATHARINE	How now!
[00:55.20]Gentleman	An't please your grace, the two great cardinals
[00:59.87]	Wait in the presence.
[01:02.25]QUEEN KATHARINE	Would they speak with me?
