[01:07.98]QUEEN KATHARINE	Pray their graces
[01:10.10]	To come near.
[01:11.78]	[Exit Gentleman]
[01:12.83]	What can be their business
[01:15.74]	With me, a poor weak woman, fall'n from favour?
[01:20.24]	I do not like their coming. Now I think on't,
[01:24.65]	They should be good men; their affairs as righteous:
[01:29.68]	But all hoods make not monks.
